=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /'pɪg/

=== Noun ===
'''pig'''

# a [[mammal]] of the genus ''Sus'', often raised on [[farm]]s for [[meat]]
# a [[greedy]] person
# a [[police]] officer (slang, usually meant as an insult)
# a selfish person.
# a difficult problem.

